channel.title: Amelia tries to host a GI Turbo [3/8] - Day 3 - Town win!
channel.description:
### Gameplay
Days will be 10 minutes long. Nights will be 5 minutes long.
### Executions
To accuse someone say **/vote [player]** This game will have Majority and Plurality
### Logs
Anyone may leave logs if they wish
### To Join
To join, simply express interest in joining by saying something like “I want to join” or “/join” or “/in” or “sign me up, coach” or whatever you want
### Rolelist:
> (For 7 players) > 1 **King** > 4 **Town** > 2 **Non-town** (at least 1 groupscum) > > > > (For 8 players) > 1 **King** > 5 **Town** > 2 **Groupscum** > > > > (For 9 Players) > 1 **King** > 6 **Town** > 2 **Non-town** (at least 1 groupscum with conversion)
# Playerlist 1. Marshal 3. Italy 4. OB_L1ght 5. Jane 6. KyoDaz 7. Apprentice 8. Chloe 9. Zone
